Package eapli.base.surveymanagement.grammar.answerverifier.generated

Interface AnswerVerifierVisitor<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - The return type of the visit operation. Use Void for operations with no return type.
    All Superinterfaces:
    org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeVisitor<T>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AnswerAdapter, AnswerVerifierBaseVisitor
    public interface AnswerVerifierVisitor<T>
extends org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeVisitor<T>
    This interface defines a complete generic visitor for a parse tree produced by AnswerVerifierParser.
